    /**
     * Exchange an authorization code for tokens (three-legged flow).
     *
     * @param code         The authorization code received from the callback.
     * @param redirectUri  The same redirect URI used in the authorization request.
     * @param codeVerifier The PKCE code verifier from {@link #getAuthorizationUrl}.
     * @throws RuntimeException If the token exchange fails.
